text: Land Hadeln is a Samtgemeinde ("collective municipality") in Cuxhaven, in Lower Saxony, Germany. Its seat is in the town of Otterndorf. It was created on 1 January 2011 from the former Samtgemeinden Hadeln and Sietland. On 1 November 2016, the Samtgemeinde Am Dobrock became a part of Land Hadeln.
